wminc-desc: Dahimmi Wiki yaɣili din su incubator
wminc-recentchanges-all: Taɣiri pala din na yɔli taɣi
wminc-prefinfo-language: A zuliya yɛltɔɣa maa bela di ko ka che wiki dahimbu dini
wminc-prefinfo-code: A ni tumdi tuun' shɛli maa kodi ISO 639
wminc-prefinfo-project: Piimi Wikipedia tuun' shɛli a ni tumdi maa kpe maa.
wminc-prefinfo-error: A piilia zuliya yɛltɔɣ' shɛli din bɔri kodi
wminc-error-move-unprefixed: Chiriŋ: Yaɣ' shɛli a ni mɔri ni a mali sɔŋ [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|nyɛla unprefixed bee di mali prefix din tuhi]].
wminc-error-wronglangcode: Chiriŋ: Yaɣili ŋɔ malila [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|zuliya yɛltɔɣa din bi tuhi]] "$1".
wminc-error-unprefixed-suggest: Error: Yaɣili ŋɔ nyɛla [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|unprefixed]]! A ni tooi nam yaɣ' palli kpe [[:$1]].
wminc-error-wiki-exists: Wiki ŋɔ nyɛla din pun beni. A ni tooi nyɛ li la yaɣili din be $1. Di yi niŋ ka wiki na yolimi nam, pahimi suɣilo guhimi hawa dibaa shɛm bee dabisa hali ka di zaa ti kana.
wminc-error-wiki-sister: Yaɣili ŋɔ bela tuun' shɛli ni din bi ka kpe. Pahimi suɣilo chami $1 kpe nti bo wiki shee.
randombytest-nopages: Gbambiɛlima yaɣa ka a wiki dahimbu ŋɔ, yuya folinsi: $1.
wminc-viewuserlang: Yuli bo tuma ŋɔ lana zuliya y~ltɔɣa ka dahim wiki
action-viewuserlang: yulimi tuma ŋɔ lana zuliya yɛltɔɣa ka dahim wiki
right-viewuserlang: yulimi tuma ŋɔ lana zuliya yɛltɔɣa ka dahim wiki
wminc-listusers-testwiki: A yuunila tum tumdiba ban niŋ bɛ wiki dahimbu biɛhigu ŋ-ŋɔ $1
wminc-search-nocreate-nopref: A bɔla ŋɔ "$1". Pahimi suɣilo niŋmi a dini [[Special:Preferences|test wiki preference]] Ka Di zuɣu che ka ti ni tooi yɛla gbambiɛlin' shɛli a ni tooi nam!
wminc-search-nocreate-suggest: Dimbɔŋɔ shee ka bo "$1".A ni tooi nam gbambiɛlinli yaɣili a wiki puuni ke [[$3]]!
wminc-searchwiki-noresults: Binshɛli kani. A ni tooi zaŋ zuliya yɛltɔɣa kodinima, yuma maŋa ni yuya din be zuliya yɛltɔɣa ni bee silimiinsili ni.
wminc-searchwiki-multiplematches: A ni bo shɛli shee maa kpinila ŋɔ
wminc-searchwiki-match-englishname: "$1" nyɛla yuli zaŋ ti $2 silimiinsili ni.
wminc-searchwiki-match-nativename: "$1" nyɛla yuli zaŋ ti $2 lala zuliya yɛltɔɣa maa ni.
wminc-fs-pagetitle: Din sɔdi che ka piligiri tuma- $1
wminc-fs-settings-title: Malimi a ni bɔri ni a wiki maa be shɛm
wminc-fs-intro: Amaraaba na  {{SITENAME}}tuuli napɔŋ yaabu ni. A nyɛla ti yɛn guli a wiki palli piligibu yɛla ni.
wminc-fs-signup-text:
A yuli yi pun sabi m-be akaunti ni, pahimi suɣilo [$1 kpɛma]. A yi na ka akaunti, pahimi suɣilo [$2 nammi akaunti].
Bɛ bi bɔrili, amaa di viɛli pam ni a mali li, ka saha biɛla ka di yɛn di a ni a nam li.
wminc-fs-settings-text:
Saha ŋɔ pahimi suɣilo chami [[Special:Preferences#mw-htmlform-i18n|your preferences]] nti taɣi wiki dahimbu kpatuɣa maa.
Din pahiri ayi maa nyɛla a tuun' shɛli a ni bɔri ni a niŋ tɔɣino maa. A yi bi mi di kodi maa, pahiki suɣilo bɔmi [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|sodoligu bukubila]] bee ka bɔmi [[{{MediaWiki:Portal-url}}|help]].
wminc-fs-userpage-text: Saha ŋɔ pahimi suɣilo nammi a tuma gbambiɛlinli yaɣili $1 ni lahabali kpeeni din jŋdi a maŋa ŋɔ. A ni tooi nya linki din tabili gbambiɛlinli ŋɔ zuɣusaa.
wminc-fs-startwiki-text: Wiki prefix maa $1.A ni tooi pili wiki maa ka di nyɛla a yɛn wiki dundɔŋ ni gbambiɛlinli yaɣili la $2.
wminc-fs-startwiki-exists-text:
A wiki maa bachi tuuli maa n-nyɛ $1. Gbambiɛlinli maa yaɣili maŋli maa be $2. A yi pa tooi laɣim tum ni zuliya yɛltɔɣ' shɛŋa ban be ʒilɛli ŋɔ puuni!
A yi bɔri ni a nam gbambiɛlin' palli, kuli sabimi di yuli niŋ binyɛra bɔbu shee adaka din be zuɣusaa ŋɔ, ka doli linki shɛli din yŋ yina maa.
wminc-infopage-welcome: Amaraaba Wikimedia Incubator ni, tuma yaɣ' shɛli   din be Wikimedia Foundation ni ([[{{MediaWiki:Aboutpage}}|About]])
wminc-infopage-missingwiki-text: Dimbɔŋɔ $1 lala zuliya y~ltɔɣa ŋɔ ni na kani.
wminc-infopage-option-startwiki: A yi bɔri ni a piligi wiki ŋɔ, pahimi suɣilo doli '''[$3 these steps]''' ni  [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|ti sodoligu bukubilal]].
wminc-infopage-option-startsister: A yi bɔri ni a pili wiki ŋɔ, a ni tooi chaŋ [$2 $1].
wminc-infopage-option-languages-existing: A ni too yuli bo [//www.$1.org existing language editions of $1].
wminc-infopage-option-sisterprojects-exi: A ni tooi yuli bo tuun' shɛŋa din pun be zuliya yɛltɔɣa ŋɔ ni.
wminc-infopage-option-sisterprojects-oth: A ni tooi yuli bo tuma din be zuliya yɛltɔɣa ŋɔ ni:
wminc-infopage-option-multilingual: A yi maai a nii, a tooi chaŋ wiki bal' bɔbidu ni.
wminc-infopage-createmainpage: Sabimi bachi ŋɔ "Gbambiɛlin' maŋli yaɣili" n-niŋ zuliya yɛltɔɣa ŋɔ ni.
wminc-infopage-contribute: A yi mi zuliya yɛltɔɣa ŋɔ, ti kpaŋsiri a ni a niŋmi tɔɣino!
wminc-infopage-status-open: Dimbɔŋɔ nyɛla sokam wiki dahimbu Wikimedia Incubator puuni
wminc-infopage-status-imported: $1 polo ka Incubator ŋɔ yina di yɔbu nyaaŋga.
wminc-infopage-status-closedsister: Yaɣili ŋɔ yomi. Chami $2 nti niŋ tɔɣino zaŋ ti wiki.
wminc-infopage-status-approved: Wiki Incubator ŋɔ nyɛla[[meta:Special:N zuliya yɛltɔɣa/zuliya yɛltɔɣa laɣingu|zuliya_yɛltɔɣa laɣingu]]  ni saɣi ti shɛli ka ni nam saha biɛla sunsuuni.
wminc-infopage-status-created: Tuma ŋɔ ny~la zuliya yɛltɔɣa laɣingu ni saɣi ti shɛli ka yi pa be $1
wminc-infopage-status-beforeincubator: Tuma ŋɔ daa nammi pɔi ka wikimedia Incubator nan yi ti pili ka be $1
wminc-infopage-error: Chiriŋ: {{#infopage}} din tooi niŋla prefix yaɣa konko.
